name: Retrofitted Machines
description:
"There are 5 million vending machines in Japan, and none of them are sleeping."

1366*2048px

This photo was taken in Tokyo in 2017. The video editing and NFT minting were done in May 2021.

About the artist:
Tokyoluv is a visual artist and street photographer who crafts lush, cyberpunk-inspired shots of cities.
